{"id":232901182,"title":"關於山道追焦","content":"不知道該發在攝影還是汽機車 \n\n各位會覺得拿手機拍追焦很怪嗎？\n最近突然燃起想拍追焦照的興趣\n因為自己本身就對拍照攝影有興趣 也有在幫忙廠商拍商品照\n近期也開始較頻繁的騎車，去涉略各種山道跟景點\n於是昨天就一如往常的跑到台七 去蹲拍\n發現大部分的人幾乎都拿單眼\n只有我拿手機在拍，頓時覺得超怪超尷尬\n無奈又沒有什麼預算換單眼，覺得自己在追焦這塊沒有那麼懂 ，用單眼又有點太浪費\n不知各位有什麼意見，可以提出來我看看 \n是否決定購入相機\n對了我尾數3085 如果也有在騎車的朋友歡迎相認一起跑哦～\n不知道第一次拍的行不行😅😅\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/ada110fb-77da-4eab-9653-bda995228467/1280.jpeg","excerpt":"不知道該發在攝影還是汽機車，各位會覺得拿手機拍追焦很怪嗎？最近突然燃起想拍追焦照的興趣，因為自己本身就對拍照攝影有興趣 也有在幫忙廠商拍商品照，近期也開始較頻繁的騎車，去涉略各種山道跟景點，於是昨天就","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"d208d1e2-6f14-429b-97b7-75a2dd4f761c","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-16T09:47:57.340Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-16T10:06:10.770Z","commentCount":13,"likeCount":24,"tags":[],"topics":["機車","檔車","追焦","跑山","攝影"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"汽機車","forumAlias":"vehicle","school":"康寧大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":24}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/ada110fb-77da-4eab-9653-bda995228467/1280.jpeg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"c276f119-44a8-4f52-bf2e-e3a8c63cc650","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/ada110fb-77da-4eab-9653-bda995228467/640.jpeg","normalizedUrl":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/ada110fb-77da-4eab-9653-bda995228467/640.jpeg","thumbnail":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/ada110fb-77da-4eab-9653-bda995228467/640.jpeg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-16T10:05:25.810Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-16T10:06:10.770Z","width":640,"height":603},{"id":"c276f119-44a8-4f52-bf2e-e3a8c63cc650","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/ada110fb-77da-4eab-9653-bda995228467/1280.jpeg","normali